metadata.name: Stanlee Genesis Certificate
metadata.description: The Stanlee's Genesis Certificate (SGC) works as the one and only VIP Whitelist token for the upcoming Stanlee's Genesis collection dropping in September 2022. Holders of the SGC will have premium access for a guaranteed mint on the project, along with a specialized cheapest mint price. Powered by BAPESCLAN, Rocketship, and POW! Join our ecosystem and build your own universe with utility that will BLOW YOUR MIND!
